    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/e8518757602a184f22fac019a292b312_5882111420563957837.png",
                "id": "talent89196",
                "key": "神里流·轉",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神里流·轉"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">瀧廻鑑花</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">瀧廻鑑花</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普通攻擊</span>造成的傷害+1，造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>變為<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：３</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/dcc79a1b8f2f01e28bdc03dd99e41038_3256191110661405680.png",
                "id": "talent76478",
                "key": "神里流·鏡花",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神里流·鏡花"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">清淨之園囿</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/07/18/7998136/0b940a837712755aebc461ec48452cb3_1953377219985946703.png",
                "id": "talent68025",
                "key": "神里流·水囿",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神里流·水囿"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召喚物在場時：</span>我方角色「普通攻擊」造成的傷害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5594174212311332663.png",
                "id": "talent68982",
                "key": "清淨之園囿",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/17/125391187/ad5eb2ee48365d340272b333689f3ebb_5946945364504065625.png",
                "title": "清淨之園囿"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/84496276/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_4042129780395997116.png",
                "id": "talent10684",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/10/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6548729744670444807.png",
